title: Photos: Dalljiet Kaur Just Shared The Most Adorable Photos With Her Son
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 30 . 2017 
Dalljiet Kaur has been the talk of the town this week after she put up some incredibly gorgeous photos of herself after her drastic weight loss. The actress lost a whopping 33 kilos through a lot of hard work and dedication… and can we just say that she looks effin’ beautiful! She has now taken to Instagram to share some photos from her photoshoot with her son and they’re too cute! Check them out.
